♪Sighing that all lives
are tied to fate♪

00:14:07.616 --> 00:14:12.544
♪Yet in this life our destined bond
is but a fleeting illusion♪

00:14:12.838 --> 00:14:14.976
♪Though drowned in love's embrace♪

00:14:15.168 --> 00:14:16.896
♪Scars now mark my weary face♪

00:14:17.223 --> 00:14:20.480
♪Love and hate through fleeting years,
memories fade with falling tears♪

00:14:22.240 --> 00:14:22.680
Gao Fu!

00:14:23.120 --> 00:14:23.680
Gao Fu!

00:14:24.160 --> 00:14:25.280
See if this is enough.

00:14:26.400 --> 00:14:27.000
It's enough.

00:14:29.960 --> 00:14:30.920
What are you doing?

00:14:31.328 --> 00:14:33.184
Didn't you say it needs fresh blood?

00:14:33.640 --> 00:14:35.560
It must be blood from immediate family.

00:14:36.000 --> 00:14:37.920
In other words, Master Lu's blood.

00:14:38.440 --> 00:14:40.280
Then take this to Lu Shi'an immediately.

00:14:40.280 --> 00:14:42.000
Once engorged,
it must be used immediately.

00:14:42.200 --> 00:14:44.440
All my running around
is just a hassle and an eyesore.

00:14:46.280 --> 00:14:47.720
Then whenever you need blood,

00:14:48.400 --> 00:14:50.640
just have someone bring Lu Shi'an over.

00:14:51.640 --> 00:14:52.000
Remember.

00:14:52.160 --> 00:14:54.080
Don't let anyone see this,

00:14:54.360 --> 00:14:55.400
especially A'man.

00:14:58.920 --> 00:14:59.640
Lady Ye,

00:15:00.640 --> 00:15:01.600
administer this to Jin.

00:15:02.560 --> 00:15:04.840
What's inside this?

00:15:04.840 --> 00:15:05.640
Leeches.

00:15:07.000 --> 00:15:08.120
They can detoxify Jin.

00:15:08.208 --> 00:15:13.664
♪Snow graces my hair as I sing,
your zither silent forever♪

00:15:18.400 --> 00:15:19.240
Be good, Jin.

00:15:19.760 --> 00:15:21.360
Drink as much as you can.

