00:15:51.410 --> 00:15:53.408
♪Time's relentless flow♪

00:15:53.504 --> 00:15:57.472
♪Leaves sorrow's lingering glow♪

00:15:58.816 --> 00:16:07.552
♪The millet-dream fades,
making strangers of us♪

